{"tid":1887325,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美議員提法案懲罰美企配合中國審查員工言論","createTime":"2020-02-19T12:34:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-19T13:02:51.000Z","uid":305299,"like":35,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"107a5a7ead22ccba6228ce739e0b10bcdad725ba","tid":1887325,"uid":305299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:34:10.000Z","msg":"【美國會採取行動 阻止美企配合中國審查】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-congress-moves-to-stop-chinese-censoring-of-americans-20200214/5288498.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fus-congress-moves-to-stop-chinese-censoring-of-americans-20200214%2F5288498.html&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5L4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=e7a1781f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/us-congress-moves-to-stop-chinese-censoring-of-americans-20200214/5288498.html</a><br />\n美國國會一個由兩黨議員組成的團體週三提出一項立法，要求防止美國企業懲罰那些對中國提出批評意見的僱員，以避免中國仰仗經濟實力來施加政治影響力。<br />\n<br />\n該法案主要發起人、印第安納州共和黨籍眾議員班克斯（Jim Banks）表示：&ldquo;只要你是美國人，或者在美國領土上，你就應該有言論自由的權利。當中國試圖將審查制度輸出到海外時，國會不會袖手旁觀。美國將繼續是自由的土地。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n這項名為《美國防止外國審查法案》(Preventing Foreign Censorship in America Act)的立法顯然是針對北京，但並不僅限於中國。該法案將禁止任何在美國運營的公司因為僱員&ldquo;與中國有關&rdquo;的言論而將其解僱或進行報復。這些言論可能涉及台灣、香港和新疆等中國政府視為敏感的話題。<br />\n<br />\n隨著中國經濟實力的壯大，那些尋求在中國做生意的外國公司面臨不斷增長的政治壓力。去年10月，全美籃球協議（NBA）休斯頓火箭隊總經理莫雷（Daryl Morey）在推特上表達了對香港抗議者的支持，這引發中國全面抵制NBA比賽，並要求火箭隊開除莫雷。<br />\n<br />\n更早些時候，范思哲、寇馳和紀梵希等國際知名品牌都為生產那些被視為損害了中國主權的T卹向中國道歉，梅賽德斯-奔馳也為在社交媒體上引用達賴喇嘛的話向中國政府道歉。<br />\n<br />\n威斯康辛州共和黨籍眾議員加拉格爾（Mike Gallagher）說：&ldquo;中國政府正越來越多地通過向外國公司施壓，要求它們懲罰或審查那些在北京方面認為不妥的話題上暢所欲言的僱員，從而控制整個自由世界的思想和言論自由。這種情況必須停止。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n該法案試圖通過約束僱傭合同，避免僱員在敏感問題上被迫保持沉默，並建立執法機制，受害者可以利用這些機制為自己辯護，並向聯邦政府報告那些屈服於專制政權壓力的公司。<br />\n<br />\n=====<br />\n如果有公司夠膽違反依條法案，有可能每次罰成十萬到一百萬美金不等<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而且法案講明適用於境外註冊，但有美國業務嘅公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />希望個法案可以盡快獲得通過喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />過咗嘅話，我睇因航仲敢唔敢亂來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，個法案內容，仲要求國務卿每年向國會提交報告，紀錄打壓員工發表撐香港新疆西藏言論嘅公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n法案內容可以睇依到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/5830/text\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.congress.gov%2Fbill%2F116th-congress%2Fhouse-bill%2F5830%2Ftext&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5L4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=ad366b34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/house-bill/5830/text</a><br />\n<br />\n希望大家可以去4位法案發起人嘅 twitter 講多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：<br />\n民主黨議員 Tom Malinowski (New Jersey) ：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/Malinowski\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FMalinowski&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5L4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=7355ca25\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/Malinowski</a><br />\n民主黨議員 Brad Sherman (California)：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/BradSherman\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FBradSherman&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5L4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=2b5e51ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/BradSherman</a><br />\n共和黨議員 Mike Gallagher (Wisconsin)：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepGallagher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepGallagher&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5L4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=0a38a226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepGallagher</a><br />\n共和黨議員 Jim Banks (Indiana)：<a href=\"https://twitter.com/RepJimBanks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRepJimBanks&d=lLWZrBwjloX75B4v2mFt5L4BfDbUEiSkD5bB26vbFoA%3D&h=41df39d9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/RepJimBanks</a>"},{"pid":"b2aa89f5e161b05552ab01e48a64b1af94bef155","tid":1887325,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:35:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75b20d4be5eb2605c2317415e525af5ce86ba614","tid":1887325,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:49:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新舊721　君子報仇，十年未晚。但此仇不報非君子<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1887317\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1887317</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c560de1224dd88db0ffe376d2366224ebcb15d92","tid":1887325,"uid":37929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:54:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16300f674c3648934db2de61a5a3ef3654eb2a3e","tid":1887325,"uid":125193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:56:02.000Z","msg":"USA USA"},{"pid":"6c811bbb2ab9b1195d6803e850b6dd94dd51759c","tid":1887325,"uid":45523,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-19T12:56:29.000Z","msg":"唔係下話<br />\n咁開心嘅事竟然發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\